{"tid":192134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬尾女子半小時4度縱火","createTime":"2017-04-08T11:14:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-08T14:12:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"26e929dfc2f49d0ee8612189b0c349a49348a1f4","tid":192134,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T11:14:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19983525&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19983525%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170408&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9ldibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=1ccafc3f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19983525%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170408&h=a921ab2f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19983525&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170408</a><br />\n<br />\n馬尾女子半小時4度縱火<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】油旺區深宵出現縱火狂徒，不足半小時內連接在4處地方縱火，消防員疲於奔命撲火。其中在南頭街有閉路電視拍到一名束馬尾的女子放火情況，警方正全力追緝。<br />\n前晚11時40分左右，旺角廣東道982號後巷一部載着雜物的手推車起火焚燒；4分鐘後，渡船街306號一間店舖門外帆布簷篷燒毀；至11時55分左右，山東街18號後巷又有一輛停泊的電單車的布冚被焚毀。至昨凌晨零時許，旺角南頭街25號一個菜檔，門外一個放有招紙的發泡膠箱突然起火，兩名途經的巴基斯坦漢發現，拍門通知對面菜館職員到場淋水將火救熄。<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n菜館閉路電視拍得一女子手持火機出現，然後點燃發泡膠箱縱火。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n持打火機邊行邊撻火<br />\n<br />\n警員稍後翻看菜館門外的閉路電視，發現一名束馬尾的女子在現場手持打火機一邊行一邊撻火，然後蹲低點火燒發泡膠箱，之後離開。<br />\n因4宗縱火案範圍僅在300米之內，警方懷疑案件均與該名女子有關及展開追緝。女狂徒年約30至40歲，身高約1.6米，當時身穿藍色上衣及藍色牛仔褲。<br />\n■記者鄭文輝"},{"pid":"ac00cf1b7737707aa1d7cc2b78d2de55fb6a0be7","tid":192134,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T11:17:01.000Z","msg":"菜館閉路電視拍得一女子手持火機出現，然後點燃發泡膠箱縱火。互聯網<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170408/large/08la7p03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170408%2Flarge%2F08la7p03.jpg&h=86c798e0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"81dd72fc36be6d89f309df52f17bf051e085c5ab","tid":192134,"uid":2889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T11:18:35.000Z","msg":"火拳艾斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b14d373dd011091ccc7bc02c4950b4531cb36b81","tid":192134,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T11:20:43.000Z","msg":"so hot<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9222ca9fcff5ee1d08761b2e7dd62463c3f9c81","tid":192134,"uid":44948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T14:11:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>菜館閉路電視拍得一女子手持火機出現，然後點燃發泡膠箱縱火。互聯網<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170408/large/08la7p03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170408%2Flarge%2F08la7p03.jpg&h=86c798e0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n清到咁實捉到人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6e718795cdb044cb92ce229ca0e6f2bcc66a39c","tid":192134,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T14:12:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>菜館閉路電視拍得一女子手持火機出現，然後點燃發泡膠箱縱火。互聯網<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170408/large/08la7p03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170408%2Flarge%2F08la7p03.jpg&h=86c798e0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n清到咁實捉到人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n清楚見到 馬尾, 火機 同發泡膠箱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/f